A Metropolitan Police officer is in a critical condition after being run over while trying to stop a speeding car in the early hours of the morning.

PC Andy Duncan, 47, was hit after signalling for the black Volkswagen Golf to pull over in Sutton, south London.

Officers this afternoon arrested a 25-year-old man on suspicion of causing serious injury while dangerous driving following the accident at around 1am.

